                <note rend="inline" type="source">724.3415/4130: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Brazil</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gibson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Rio de Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-09-15T20:00:00-03:00"
                            >September 15, 1934—8 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 8:30 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>225. My 224. After further conversation this afternoon I am authorized to say
                    that despite irritation and concern Brazil is in this mediation as long as [we?]
                    desire her cooperation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gibson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
